*Pitao* je zašto se njegova majka nije pojavila na proslavi. (He asked why his mother didn't show up at the celebration.)

*Pitati* će ga zašto nije hteo da dođe. (He will ask him why he didn't want to come.)

*Pitam* se da li će biti dovoljno vremena za sve. (I wonder if there will be enough time for everything.)

*Pitao* sam ga da li je mogao da mi pomogne. (I asked him if he could help me.)

*Pitala* sam se da li je to pravo vreme za odlazak. (I asked myself if this was the right time to leave.)

*Pitali* su ga da li će učestvovati u konkursu. (They asked him if he was going to participate in the contest.)